{"id":"cli/lint","title":"ng lint","contents":"\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/lint\", \"name\": \"lint\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-lint\">ng lint<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/lint#ng-lint\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    <p>在給定專案資料夾中的 Angular 應用程式程式碼上執行 linting 工具。</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">lint</span> [<var>project</var>]\n</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------mode_edit--code--------描述----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/lint/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/lint/long-description.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        描述\n    </h2>\n    <p>該命令採用可選的專案名稱，在 <code>angular.json</code> 工作區配置檔案的 <code>projects</code> 部分中指定。當未提供專案名稱時，為所有專案執行 <code>lint</code> 建構器。</p>\n<p>要使用 <code>ng lint</code> 命令，請使用 <code>ng add</code> 來新增實現 linting 特性的套件。新增包會自動更新你的工作區配置，新增 lint <a href=\"guide/cli-builder\">CLI 建構器</a>。例如：</p>\n<code-example language=\"json\">\n \"projects\": { \"my-project\": { ... \"architect\": { ... \"lint\": { \"builder\": \"@angular-eslint/builder:lint\", \"options\": {} } } } }\n</code-example>\n\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">引數</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"width:15%\">引數</th>\n      <th style=\"width:40%\">說明</th>\n      <th>值型別</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">project</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>要建構的專案名。可以是應用或庫。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">選項</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th style=\"width:15%\">選項</th>\n    <th style=\"width:40%\">說明</th>\n    <th>值型別</th>\n    <th>預設值</th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--configuration</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>逗號分隔列表格式的一個或多個命名建構器配置，在 angular.json 的 <code>configurations</code> 部分中指定。建構器使用命名配置來執行給定的目標。有關更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/workspace-config#alternate-build-configurations\">https://angular.io/guide/workspace-config#alternate-build-configurations</a>。</p>\n\n      <p><span class=\"cli-aliases\">別名:</span> -c</p>\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在控制檯顯示關於本命令的幫助資訊。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/lint#ng-lint\n - guide/cli-builder\n - https://angular.io/guide/workspace-config#alternate-build-configurations\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/lint/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/lint/long-description.md\n-->"}